1
00:00:35,233 --> 00:00:38,800
(Adapted from Tale of Herding God
on Qidian Chinese Network
under China Literature, Author: Zhaizhu)

2
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:24,066
(Tales of Herding Gods)

3
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:28,999
You've been staring
at the screen for ages.

4
00:02:29,233 --> 00:02:30,765
Don't just watch.

5
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:34,099
Follow the series, drop coins,
and hit like.

6
00:02:34,433 --> 00:02:36,765
I want your triple support.

7
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:41,532
I want it right now.

8
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:48,900
(The story depicted in this animation is entirely fictional)

9
00:02:49,966 --> 00:02:54,700
(Episode 79)
(The Calamity Arc: Heavenly King of Zhenhai)

10
00:03:01,833 --> 00:03:04,466
Grandpa Deaf has been gone six days
without a word.

11
00:03:04,833 --> 00:03:06,632
There are only three days left
till New Year.

12
00:03:06,833 --> 00:03:08,666
They've been gone too long.

13
00:03:08,833 --> 00:03:10,966
Do you think something happened
on the way?

14
00:03:13,633 --> 00:03:14,999
Let's go to the source of the Yong River
and find them.

15
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:17,766
Even someone as strong as Master
didn't come back.

16
00:03:17,767 --> 00:03:19,432
What good would it do if we went?

17
00:03:20,033 --> 00:03:22,232
Hu Ling'er, go to Xianglong City
and report this.

18
00:03:22,533 --> 00:03:23,832
Get the Sacred Sect's experts moving.

19
00:03:24,133 --> 00:03:26,132
Have them gather news
and track down clues.

20
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:28,499
Big Dragon and I will head up
along the Yong River

21
00:03:29,033 --> 00:03:30,432
and go find the entrance
to the Dark Realm.

22
00:03:39,933 --> 00:03:41,232
Something's changing again
in the distance.

23
00:03:41,867 --> 00:03:43,399
Looks like we have quite a few guests.

24
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,699
We'd better prepare more thoroughly.

25
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:48,532
So no one says people from
the Great Wasteland lack manners.

26
00:05:09,133 --> 00:05:09,832
Demon King.

27
00:05:11,100 --> 00:05:12,499
You're from
the Heavenly Demon Race too, right?

28
00:05:13,933 --> 00:05:16,532
You want to use my power?

29
00:05:16,633 --> 00:05:17,232
No!

30
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,566
If you treat me a little better,

31
00:05:19,633 --> 00:05:20,832
I might agree to it.

32
00:05:21,167 --> 00:05:22,632
But you hit me for no reason,

33
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:23,966
and that really annoyed me.

34
00:05:24,767 --> 00:05:26,832
If you help me find the elders
in the village,

35
00:05:27,033 --> 00:05:28,266
I'll set you free.

36
00:05:28,933 --> 00:05:30,232
How does that sound?

37
00:05:32,833 --> 00:05:33,999
Deal.

38
00:05:42,667 --> 00:05:44,466
Young Master,
I'm off to deliver the message.

39
00:06:06,067 --> 00:06:06,532
Let's go!

40
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,632
Everyone who searched this area is dead.

41
00:06:27,300 --> 00:06:28,332
Something's off.

42
00:06:35,933 --> 00:06:39,632
This village is huge,
but there's not a soul in sight.

43
00:06:47,667 --> 00:06:49,932
This whole village is full of treasures.

44
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,066
Go!

45
00:07:31,233 --> 00:07:32,766
We can't go into this village.

46
00:07:33,933 --> 00:07:35,366
Hong, move!

47
00:07:44,733 --> 00:07:45,266
It's getting dark.

48
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,832
There are ruins up ahead.
Let's head there!

49
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:49,399
Senior Brother Chiyun.

50
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:52,932
After spending some time training
in the Great Wasteland,

51
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:57,299
I'm still shaken
by all its strange wonders.

52
00:08:58,567 --> 00:09:02,666
Even these ruins have
such a grand Heavenly King statue.

53
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,266
Junior Sister,

54
00:09:06,633 --> 00:09:09,499
my disciple Shao Yuan
was just discussing this with me.

55
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:13,332
Many people from the Great Wasteland come to
offer incense for the Heavenly King statue.

56
00:09:13,500 --> 00:09:15,632
This statue clearly has
an extraordinary origin.

57
00:09:36,833 --> 00:09:38,532
There's something off
about these Daoists.

58
00:09:38,733 --> 00:09:39,532
I know.

59
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:43,066
One of the female Daoists
is Long Jiaonan.

60
00:10:05,167 --> 00:10:08,167
(Tales of Herding Gods)

61
00:10:11,533 --> 00:10:15,299
Should we make the first move?

62
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,899
The Great Wasteland has its rules.

63
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:21,132
When darkness falls,
no one fights inside the ruins.

64
00:10:39,867 --> 00:10:42,399
There is an aura
of the True God in the dark.

65
00:10:42,667 --> 00:10:43,666
That's a huge disturbance.

66
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:46,999
Why is tonight different from usual?

67
00:10:47,933 --> 00:10:49,532
When the darkness fell just now,

68
00:10:49,867 --> 00:10:52,299
the giant beast bones in the ruins
came back to life,

69
00:10:52,433 --> 00:10:53,499
turning into the Beast God,

70
00:10:53,767 --> 00:10:54,699
and walked out of the ruins.

71
00:10:56,067 --> 00:10:58,399
It is fighting demonic monsters
in the dark.

72
00:11:04,133 --> 00:11:05,732
It's already past midnight.

73
00:11:24,900 --> 00:11:27,099
Clear the way.

74
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:32,166
Clear the way.

75
00:11:32,433 --> 00:11:36,400
(Silence)

76
00:11:37,333 --> 00:11:39,100
(Clear the way)

77
00:12:09,567 --> 00:12:11,932
Silence!

78
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:19,499
Heavenly King of Zhenhai,

79
00:12:19,633 --> 00:12:23,832
Ao Zhen, the East Sea Dragon King, has used
the heavenly calamity to stir chaos.

80
00:12:24,267 --> 00:12:26,432
His Majesty has sent an order
from Worry-Free Land.

81
00:12:26,433 --> 00:12:28,232
We were ordered to come here

82
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:31,432
to help you take him down!

83
00:12:33,233 --> 00:12:34,499
Worry-Free Land.

84
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:39,032
It's been in chaos
for over twenty thousand years.

85
00:13:45,267 --> 00:13:47,766
And this guy still dares to rise up.

86
00:13:48,967 --> 00:13:50,066
Bring me my blade!

87
00:14:15,133 --> 00:14:17,166
Where is my mount?

88
00:14:22,767 --> 00:14:23,999
Kylin steed,

89
00:14:24,233 --> 00:14:25,699
why won't you move forward?

90
00:14:26,267 --> 00:14:27,632
Carry out the order now.

91
00:14:28,667 --> 00:14:30,199
Ride out with me!

92
00:16:02,967 --> 00:16:06,166
Go back to Worry-Free Land
and report to His Majesty.

93
00:16:16,533 --> 00:16:18,566
I have fulfilled my mission.

94
00:16:19,167 --> 00:16:23,066
The rebel leader
has already been taken down!

95
00:16:24,067 --> 00:16:25,366
Aye!

96
00:16:50,767 --> 00:16:52,632
Big Dragon, what's wrong?

97
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:59,332
I dreamed I was carrying
a God King on my back.

98
00:16:59,433 --> 00:17:02,899
We charged
into a fierce, chaotic battlefield.

99
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:05,732
Countless dragons came at me.

100
00:17:06,067 --> 00:17:08,599
But the God King on my back
cut them down with his blade.

101
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:12,766
That God King cut off
a Dragon King's head!

102
00:17:13,633 --> 00:17:15,899
That dream felt so real.

103
00:17:17,633 --> 00:17:21,399
This Heavenly King statue really did
strike down an East Sea Dragon King.

104
00:17:21,900 --> 00:17:25,299
The blood on the blade
is the East Sea Dragon King's blood.

105
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,966
Where exactly is Worry-Free Land?

106
00:17:41,933 --> 00:17:42,499
Let's go.

107
00:17:57,767 --> 00:18:15,033
(Zhenhai Guandi Temple)

